**Guardsman** | Townsfolk Killing | Limited
__Basics__
Once per game, at night, the Guardsman may choose to be on guard for the rest of the night.
While on guard any attacks fail and the attacker is counterattacked instead.
__Details__
Once per game, at night, the Guardsman may choose to be on guard for the rest of the night. This is an immediate ability.
If the guardsman is attacked while on guard, they survive and attack whoever attacked them.
If they attack a townsfolk aligned player, the Guardsman dies at the end of the next night.

__Simplified__
The guardsman may go on guard once at night. If attacked they survive and counterattack the attacker.
If they kill a townsfolk aligned player, the Guardsman dies at the end of the next night.

__Formalized__
Immediate Night: Protect @Self from `Attacks` through Passive Defense (~Phase) [Quantity: 1]
On Passive Defense: 
  • Attack @Attacker
  • @Attacker->Alignment is `Townsfolk`: Apply `Marker` to @Self
Passive End Night: True Kill @Self [Attribute: Marker]

__Card__
An on guard Guardsman is a living Guardsman.
